    {
      "id": "ma9a2ed2f30224a10",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 888,
      "width": 312.62,
      "height": 237.60000000000002,
      "text": "# Project Structure\n├── src/          # Código fonte (Go 1.22)\n├── internal/     # Pacotes internos\n├── api/          # Definições OpenAPI\n└── docs/         # Documentação detalhada\n\n## Code Conventions\n- Nomes de função em camelCase\n- Testes com testify + table-driven\n- Commits: conventional commits\n- Lint: golangci-lint com config em .golangci.yml\n\n## Links\n- Guia de Arquitetura: /docs/architecture.md\n- Runbooks: /docs/runbooks/\n- Postmortems: /docs/postmortems/",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
